  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-provider AI support (Claude, GPT, Gemini, Grok, DeepSeek, and 300+ models)",
    "Interactive terminal-based development environment",
    "Semantic code search with workspace indexing",
    "Model Context Protocol (MCP) for extensible tool integration",
    "Multi-agent workflows for complex tasks",
    "Custom commands and slash commands",
    "Git integration with AI-powered commit messages",
    "Shell integration with ZSH plugin and theme",
    "Conversation management and history",
    "Configurable via forge.yaml with custom rules"
